adidas Australia Privacy Policy
WHAT DOES THIS PRIVACY POLICY TELL YOU?
WHICH ADIDAS ENTITIES COLLECT AND MANAGE YOUR PERSONAL INFORMATION?
WHO IS THE PRIVACY OFFICER FOR ADIDAS?
WHAT PERSONAL INFORMATION DOES ADIDAS COLLECT AND HOLD?
HOW DOES ADIDAS COLLECT YOUR PERSONAL INFORMATION?
WHAT ARE THE PURPOSES FOR WHICH ADIDAS COLLECTS, HOLDS, USES AND DISCLOSES PERSONAL INFORMATION?
WHAT DOES ADIDAS DO WITH PERSONAL INFORMATION COLLECTED THROUGH WWW.ADIDAS.COM.AU AND OUR DIFFERENT PLATFORMS, PORTALS AND APPLICATIONS?
HOW CAN YOU UNSUBSCRIBE FROM MARKETING MESSAGES?
WHO IS YOUR PERSONAL INFORMATION DISCLOSED TO AND IS YOUR PERSONAL INFORMATION DISCLOSED OUTSIDE OF AUSTRALIA?
