adidas New Zealand Privacy policy
Updated on 1 August 2024
WHAT DOES THIS PRIVACY POLICY TELL YOU?
WHICH ADIDAS ENTITIES COLLECT AND MANAGE YOUR PERSONAL INFORMATION?
WHO IS THE DATA PROTECTION OFFICER FOR ADIDAS?
