WHAT ARE THE PURPOSES FOR WHICH ADIDAS COLLECTS, HOLDS, USES AND DISCLOSES PERSONAL INFORMATION?
WHAT DOES ADIDAS DO WITH PERSONAL INFORMATION COLLECTED THROUGH
WWW.ADIDAS.CO.NZ
, THE ADIDAS APP AND OUR DIFFERENT PLATFORMS, PORTALS AND APPLICATIONS, AND WHY (PURPOSE, PROCESSING)?
8. HOW CAN YOU UNSUBSCRIBE FROM MARKETING MESSAGES?
